623
00:15:17,400 --> 00:15:18,040
Three?

624
00:15:18,040 --> 00:15:18,600
I'm here.

625
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:19,400
Sorry, my bad.

626
00:15:19,640 --> 00:15:21,240
Three is listening.

627
00:15:21,240 --> 00:15:22,560
Three.

628
00:15:22,560 --> 00:15:23,680
Three's a Glutton.

629
