632
00:15:27,280 --> 00:15:28,520
Four, say something.

633
00:15:28,520 --> 00:15:28,960
Four.

634
00:15:29,760 --> 00:15:30,240
Four.

635
00:15:30,720 --> 00:15:32,440
Why is four taking so long?

636
00:15:32,500 --> 00:15:34,420
(Loving the chaos)

637
00:15:37,160 --> 00:15:37,960
(Stirring the pot)
Go on.

638
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:38,720
