706
00:17:25,920 --> 00:17:27,200
Just leaning back?

707
00:17:27,200 --> 00:17:28,600
That makes no sense.

708
00:17:28,920 --> 00:17:30,160
So, her voice

709
00:17:30,160 --> 00:17:32,560
