I'm exhausted.

711
00:17:33,760 --> 00:17:35,040
We were playing in the water all afternoon.

712
00:17:35,040 --> 00:17:35,880
I was like this.

713
00:17:35,880 --> 00:17:36,360
Three.

714
00:17:36,360 --> 00:17:37,400
Just like this.

715
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:38,280
Seven.

716
00:17:38,280 --> 00:17:40,320
Actually, I was sitting right by Yang.

717
00:17:40,320 --> 00:17:41,480
She never even said ten.

718
00:17:42,520 --> 00:17:43,400
You didn't hear it.

719
00:17:43,400 --> 00:17:44,560
She definitely said ten.

720
00:17:44,560 --> 00:17:45,800
I said ten.

721
00:17:45,800 --> 00:17:47,200
My voice was low.

722
00:17:47,200 --> 00:17:49,480
You've let love cloud your judgment again.

723
00:17:49,480 --> 00:17:51,640
Yeah, you've let love
cloud your judgment again.

724
00:17:51,640 --> 00:17:52,520
Listen to me.

725
00:17:52,520 --> 00:17:53,280
When she said ten,

726
00:17:53,280 --> 00:17:54,720
