755
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:35,360
Is it me?

756
00:18:35,900 --> 00:18:37,340
(Didn't see that coming, huh?)

757
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:40,160
See?

758
00:18:40,160 --> 00:18:41,120
It's the three of us?

759
00:18:42,820 --> 00:18:44,540
