770
00:19:03,960 --> 00:19:05,240
I think Jiawei did a great job.

771
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:06,520
He was good.

772
00:19:06,520 --> 00:19:07,200
Jiawei.

773
00:19:07,200 --> 00:19:07,840
Yeah, Jiawei.

774
00:19:08,200 --> 00:19:10,720
