Congrats to Yang Tinghong and Huang Jiawei.

775
00:19:10,720 --> 00:19:14,000
You will be the captains
for the next team challenge.

776
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:18,000
The second round is a team match.

777
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:20,000
The male and female MVPs from Round 1

778
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:21,840
