790
00:19:37,600 --> 00:19:37,920
Yang.

791
00:19:37,920 --> 00:19:38,600
I'll pick Enda.

792
00:19:39,000 --> 00:19:39,640
Him?

793
00:19:39,640 --> 00:19:40,220
