794
00:19:40,220 --> 00:19:41,620
(Happy)

795
00:19:42,060 --> 00:19:42,740
(I'll pick you later, bro.)

796
00:19:42,740 --> 00:19:43,820
(Got it.)

797
00:19:43,980 --> 00:19:44,360
(Come on.)

798
00:19:44,360 --> 00:19:44,800
What?

799
00:19:44,800 --> 00:19:45,520
(Shocked)
What?

800
00:19:45,600 --> 00:19:46,200
Wanna team up with me?

801
00:19:46,200 --> 00:19:47,060
I want her.

802
00:19:47,200 --> 00:19:48,350
(My friend picked me.)
She's joining my team.

803
00:19:49,700 --> 00:19:50,700
(Frazzled)

804
00:19:51,180 --> 00:19:52,680
(Then I pick you.)

805
00:19:52,680 --> 00:19:53,400
Is it my turn now?

806
00:19:53,400 --> 00:19:54,200
(Come on, girl!)
Yijia.

807
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:01,560
My turn now?

808
00:20:02,000 --> 00:20:02,880
Pick a guy.

809
00:20:02,880 --> 00:20:03,780
(Make the gender ratio even.)

810
00:20:04,080 --> 00:20:05,320
She picked you.

811
00:20:06,040 --> 00:20:06,520
Okay.

812
00:20:06,520 --> 00:20:08,320
Alright, no worries. Just pick whoever.

813
00:20:08,480 --> 00:20:09,120
Then I'll pick

814
00:20:10,040 --> 00:20:10,800
