Good.

819
00:20:14,550 --> 00:20:15,000
We've got this.

820
00:20:15,000 --> 00:20:15,840
Yeah, okay.

821
00:20:16,360 --> 00:20:17,160
Yeah.

822
00:20:18,700 --> 00:20:19,340
