823
00:20:20,080 --> 00:20:21,000
Guanjie, right?

824
00:20:21,920 --> 00:20:22,680
My bestie.

825
00:20:22,680 --> 00:20:23,700
(Bestie, here.)

826
00:20:24,040 --> 00:20:25,040
Then I'll pick Yan.

827
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:28,300
Come on.

828
00:20:28,300 --> 00:20:28,770
("I Know You Best")

829
00:20:28,770 --> 00:20:30,500
(Team Huang: Lu Yanting,
Yang Tianyu, Wu Guanjie, Wu Yihan)

830
00:20:30,500 --> 00:20:32,300
(Team Yang: Zhao Enda, Chen Yijia,
Ding Wanning, Zhu Huiyan)

831
00:20:32,360 --> 00:20:33,360
"I Know You Best"

832
00:20:33,360 --> 00:20:34,280
game rules:

833
00:20:34,280 --> 00:20:36,080
On the whiteboard are photos

834
00:20:36,080 --> 00:20:37,280
