839
00:20:45,480 --> 00:20:46,640
One point for a correct match,

840
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:47,680
and none for a wrong one.

841
00:20:47,680 --> 00:20:48,560
Find the right part.

842
00:20:48,560 --> 00:20:50,880
Match the part to the person.

843
00:20:51,720 --> 00:20:52,720
You got it right.

844
00:20:52,720 --> 00:20:54,000
Enda guessed it correctly.

845
00:20:55,940 --> 00:20:59,860
