846
00:20:59,880 --> 00:21:01,880
Come on, dear.

847
00:21:01,880 --> 00:21:02,480
Hurry up.

848
00:21:02,480 --> 00:21:03,000
Whose is this?

849
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:04,200
