854
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:10,960
Whose is this? Yijia's?

855
00:21:10,960 --> 00:21:11,420
Yijia, I think.

856
00:21:13,420 --> 00:21:15,100
No, my collarbone doesn't look like that.

857
00:21:15,120 --> 00:21:15,680
Jiayi.

858
00:21:15,680 --> 00:21:16,700
I said the wrong name.

859
00:21:16,700 --> 00:21:18,300
The hair color gives it away, definitely Jiayi.

860
00:21:18,300 --> 00:21:20,940
(Identified by hair color: Jiayi)

861
00:21:20,980 --> 00:21:23,580
(Looking around)

862
00:21:23,720 --> 00:21:24,240
This is mine.

863
00:21:24,340 --> 00:21:26,380
(Chen Yijia identified her own body part.)

864
00:21:26,380 --> 00:21:27,380
(Yijia)

865
00:21:27,600 --> 00:21:28,480
This one, this one.

866
00:21:28,960 --> 00:21:29,520
Whose is this?

867
00:21:30,220 --> 00:21:31,700
(Who are you supposed to be?)

868
00:21:31,720 --> 00:21:32,840
(I know my bro too well)
Lu.

869
00:21:32,840 --> 00:21:34,300
(Enda)

870
00:21:34,300 --> 00:21:35,460
(Another team)
Whose mouth is this?

871
00:21:35,460 --> 00:21:38,400
(Still totally puzzled)

872
00:21:38,400 --> 00:21:39,200
This one feels like mine.

873
00:21:39,200 --> 00:21:39,410
Yijia.

874
00:21:39,410 --> 00:21:40,480
(Quickly identifying the owner)

875
00:21:40,480 --> 00:21:41,080
That's you, right?

876
00:21:41,520 --> 00:21:42,560
